[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      156[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[39m  155, 157[0m:[39m[49m ### Prerequisites
[0m[49m[39m  156, 158[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[39m  157, 159[0m:[39m[49m | Requirement | Details |
